    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes an Extension Mechanisms for DNS (EDNS0) option that is in active use to carry information about the network that originated a DNS query and the network for which the subsequent response can be cached.  Since it has some known operational and privacy shortcomings, a revision will be worked through the IETF for improvement.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
